snippet.title: Autopsy Simulator - Official Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
The latest trailer for Autopsy Simulator provides a look into the tone of this horror/thriller medical simulator, as well as several of the bodies you'll be performing your macabre work on throughout the course of the game.

#IGN #IGNExpo2022
